RACE.FOOTNOTES: MORE THAN CHANCEY lugged in midway, best. LADY OF STEL broke in, game 2nd. TEMPTING COURAGE bumped hind early, drifted in. SUPREME even effort. ELDAAFIRST DARK bumped/in tight early. GALENANA came in/multiple bumps early. SR IACOCCA bumped/bothered start, steadied late. STEWARDS INQUIRY, The Stewards conducted an inquiry following the running of the sixth race for a review of two incidents, both incidents involving the #6 Galenana (Ruben Lozano- sixth) and #5 SR Iacocca (Henry Lopez, who finished seventh). The first incident took place at the start when #6 Galenana broke in sharply and made contact with #5 SR Iacocca causing the latter to check and lose ground. The second incident taking place near the 1/16th pole of the 300 yard event, when #6 Galenana veered out sharply in front of #5 Sr Iacocca forcing the latter to take up, lose momentum and the opportunity of a better placing. The Stewards decided unanimously to disqualify #6 Galenana from sixth to seventh.
